{"pageContext":{"notebook":"Web Dev","section":"webpack","page":{"id":"0-3ad9f81475beaf478c856d1a4ed7d82c!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2218","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-3ad9f81475beaf478c856d1a4ed7d82c!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2218","createdTime":"2019-01-06T07:50:56.813Z","title":"Dev Server 구동하기","createdByAppId":"","links":{"oneNoteEmbedUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!1937&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28webpack.one%7C1ddf611b-d9d0-5344-83d0-4e44f3e1f9bc%2FDev%20Server%20%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%99%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0%7Cd6193c3a-82ae-8543-aea1-703bc65567a6%2F%29"},"oneNoteClientUrl":{"href":"onenote:https://d.docs.live.net/bc575ab8e2ab9833/Documents/Web%20Dev/webpack.one#Dev%20Server%20%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%99%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0&section-id=1ddf611b-d9d0-5344-83d0-4e44f3e1f9bc&page-id=d6193c3a-82ae-8543-aea1-703bc65567a6&end"},"oneNoteWebUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!1937&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28webpack.one%7C1ddf611b-d9d0-5344-83d0-4e44f3e1f9bc%2FDev%20Server%20%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%99%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0%7Cd6193c3a-82ae-8543-aea1-703bc65567a6%2F%29"}},"contentUrl":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-3ad9f81475beaf478c856d1a4ed7d82c!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2218/content","lastModifiedTime":"2019-01-06T08:28:00Z","parentSection@odata.context":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/$metadata#me/notes/sections('0-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212218')/pages('0-3ad9f81475beaf478c856d1a4ed7d82c%211-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212218')/parentSection(id,name,self)/$entity","parentSection":{"id":"0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2218","name":"webpack","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/sections/0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2218"},"content":"       우선,        Webpack.config.js의 mode의 value가 development가 되어 있어야 한다.        Development Tool을 이용해서 Create-react-app의 npm run start 의 기능을 직접 구현하고자 한다. 3가지 중에 한가지를 택해서 구현을 하면 된다고 한다.         Webpack's watch mode (Webpack's watch mode)           package.json에 script로 webpack --watch를 추가하거나, npx로 실행한다.                     << package.json >>        …        \"scripts\": {￼+  \"start\" : \"webpack --watch\"￼}                              << cli >>￼$ npx webpack --watch                            webpack-dev-server (Using webpack-dev-server)           Webpack-dev-server을 npm에서 설치한 후,                     $ npm install --save-dev webpack-dev-server                   Webpack.config.js에서 devServer에다가 옵션을 추가한 후,      package.json에 script로 webpack-dev-server --open를 추가하거나, npx로 실행한다.                     << webpack.config.js >>        …        + devServer: {￼+  contentBase : __dirname + '/dist'￼+  ( 기본 포트는 8080 이며, customize하려면 port 속성을 넣으면 됨 )￼+ }                                                << package.json >>        …        \"scripts\": {￼+. \"start\" : \"webpack-dev-server --open\"￼}                              << cli >>￼$ npx webpack-dev-server --open                   더 상세한 옵션은 여기에서 확인               webpack-dev-middleware (Using webpack-dev-middleware)           Webpack-dev-server 안에서 돌아가는 wrapper라고 하는데, 각각의 패키지에 다른 설정들을 건드릴 수 있게 해 준다고 한다.                         ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:48px;top:139px;width:576px\">\n\t\t\t<h1 lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-size:16pt;color:#1e4e79;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC6B0;&#xC120;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">,</span></h1>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Webpack.config.js<span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span> mode<span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span> value<span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC00;</span> development<span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC00;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB418;&#xC5B4;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC788;&#xC5B4;&#xC57C;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;</span>.</h2>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Development Tool<span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC744;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC774;&#xC6A9;&#xD574;&#xC11C;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">Create-react-app</span><span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span> npm run start <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC758;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAE30;&#xB2A5;&#xC744;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC9C1;&#xC811;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAD6C;&#xD604;&#xD558;&#xACE0;&#xC790;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;</span>. 3<span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAC00;&#xC9C0;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xC911;&#xC5D0;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD55C;&#xAC00;&#xC9C0;&#xB97C;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD0DD;&#xD574;&#xC11C;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xAD6C;&#xD604;&#xC744;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD558;&#xBA74;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xB41C;&#xB2E4;&#xACE0;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic\">&#xD55C;&#xB2E4;</span>.</h2>\n\t\t\t<ol>\n\t\t\t\t<li><p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;font-weight:bold\">Webpack&apos;s watch mode (</span><a href=\"https://webpack.js.org/guides/development/#using-watch-mode\" lang=\"ko-KR\" style=\"font-family:Malgun Gothic;fo